@startuml
!include ../../templates/styles/_style_seq.puml
autonumber

title Riddle: A, I, B on the pipe

actor Читатель as reader
participant Книга as book
participant Труба as pipe
participant A as a
participant I as i
participant B as b

== Question ==
reader -> book : Who remains on the pipe?
activate book
note right of book
    Restore state
    from riddle conditions
end note

== Initial state ==
group A, I, B are on the pipe
    book -> pipe : place(A, I, B)
    activate pipe
    pipe --> book : state = [A, I, B]
    deactivate pipe
end

== Events ==
    a ->> pipe : fall()
    activate pipe
    pipe --> book : state = [I, B]
    deactivate pipe

    b ->> pipe : disappear()
    activate pipe
    pipe --> book : state = [I]
    deactivate pipe

== Answer ==
    book -> pipe : whoRemains()
    activate pipe
    pipe --> book : I
    deactivate pipe

    book --> reader : I remains on the pipe
deactivate book

@enduml
